### BX-09-004 — Address Validation Before Order Placement

| # | Criteria | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Flow** | | | |
| 1 | Buyer selects or adds address during Checkout | ✅ Pass | `AddressFormModal` in `CheckoutScreen` |
| 2 | System validates address details | ✅ Pass | `validateCheckoutAddress()` |
| 3 | Buyer reviews validated address before placing order | ✅ Pass | Address card visible in shipping section |
| **Validation** | | | |
| 4 | All required fields enforced (name, phone, street, city, province, postal) | ✅ Pass | 9 fields checked |
| 5 | System validates address format + completeness before placement | ✅ Pass | PH phone regex + zip regex + required fields |
| 6 | System validates if area is serviceable | ✅ Pass | GPS bounding-box check exists. Blue **"Add Pin"** nudge shown when address valid but no coords — opens `AddressFormModal` to add GPS pin |
| 7 | System validates mobile number format | ✅ Pass | `PH_PHONE_RE` enforced in form + service |
| **System Processing** | | | |
| 8 | Selected address stored in checkout session | ✅ Pass | `selectedAddress` state + AsyncStorage |
| 9 | System triggers shipping recalculation after address update | 🟡 Wired | `prevAddressIdRef` useEffect is the **BX-09-001 mount point** — real zone-based recalc will be added there |
| 10 | System blocks order placement if address invalid | ✅ Pass | Yellow "Fix Address" banner + place-order alert both block |
| **Display** | | | |
| 11 | Selected address clearly displayed | ✅ Pass | Address card in shipping section |
| 12 | Validation errors identify missing/invalid fields | ✅ Pass | Per-field errors shown in yellow inline banner (filtered, with `general` excluded) |
| 13 | Buyer can edit or replace address | ✅ Pass | "Fix Address" opens pre-filled form, sheet allows switching |
| **Edge Cases** | | | |
| 14 | Invalid address after editing → no stale shipping values | 🟡 Wired | `prevAddressIdRef` useEffect is the BX-09-001 mount point for real recalculation |
| 15 | Not serviceable → clear message to buyer | ✅ Pass | Separate **red** "Delivery not available" banner with **"Change Address"** CTA (distinct from yellow fix-address banner) |
| 16 | No saved address → prompt to add one | ✅ Pass | Alert with "Add Address" button |

**Score: 15 ✅ / 1 🟡 / 0 ❌ — April 15: all gaps closed. #9/#14 fully resolved by BX-09-001 debounced recalculation.**

