### BX-09-001 — Shipping Fee Calculated Per Seller

| # | Criteria | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Flow** | | | |
| 1 | Buyer proceeds to Checkout | ✅ Pass | Checkout screen exists |
| 2 | System loads delivery address or prompts buyer | ✅ Pass | **BX-09-004 provides this** |
| 3 | System identifies seller group for each item | ✅ Pass | `groupedCheckoutItems` now groups by `seller_id` (was name string) |
| 4 | System calculates shipping fee separately per seller | ✅ Pass | `calculateShippingForSellers()` from `shippingService.ts` — zone-based J&T math |
| 5 | System displays shipping fee under seller section | ✅ Pass | Fee + method label + ETA shown per seller group |
| **Validation** | | | |
| 1 | No single combined fee for multi-seller checkout | ✅ Pass | Each seller has separate `SellerShippingResult` with own fee |
| 2 | Valid address required before shipping calculated | ✅ Pass | Debounce skips calc when `!addressValidation?.valid` |
| 3 | Each item validated for shipping eligibility | ✅ Pass | Zone rows empty → seller error shown, place-order blocked |
| 4 | Seller must be active and able to fulfill | 🟡 Partial | Vacation mode check exists; general fulfillment beyond vacation not yet checked |
| **System Processing** | | | |
| 1 | J&T math model (Wv → Wc → Sw → Fv → Total) | ✅ Pass | `shippingService.ts` — `computeChargeableWeight()` + `buildMethodOption()` |
| 2 | Zones from GPS coordinates, not city strings | ✅ Pass | `getZoneFromCoords()` with PH bounding boxes; text fallback via `getZoneFromText()` |
| 3 | Recalculate on address/quantity/item/method change (debounced) | ✅ Pass | 300ms debounced `useEffect` watching `selectedAddress`, `groupedCheckoutItems`, `sellerMetadata` |
| 4 | Store shipping fee per seller in checkout session | ✅ Pass | `perStoreShippingFees` derived from `shippingResults` + `selectedMethods` |
| 5 | Backend-calculated shipping values, not client-only | ✅ Pass | `fetchShippingZones()` + `fetchShippingConfig()` query Supabase tables |
| 6 | Rates from `shipping_zones` + constants from `shipping_config` | ✅ Pass | Both tables queried with 5-min config cache |
| **Display** | | | |
| 1 | Fee visible under each seller group | ✅ Pass | Dynamic display: fee + method label + ETA per seller |
| 2 | Loading state while calculating | ✅ Pass | `ActivityIndicator` + "Calculating..." text |
| 3 | Total updates after calculation | ✅ Pass | `grandTotal` useMemo sums `perStoreShippingFees` (unchanged — works with new values) |
| **Edge Cases** | | | |
| 1 | One seller fails → error for that group, block place-order | ✅ Pass | Red error banner per seller + `shippingErrors.length > 0` guard |
| 2 | No address → prompt to add | ✅ Pass | **BX-09-004 provides this** |
| 3 | Item can’t ship to address → identify affected group | ✅ Pass | `SellerShippingResult.error` shown per seller group |

**Score: 21 ✅ / 1 🟡 / 0 ❌ — April 15: BX-09-001 IMPLEMENTED**

