### BX-09-002 — Choose Shipping Method Per Seller

| # | Criteria | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Flow** | | | |
| 1-7 | Full method selection flow | ✅ Pass | `ShippingMethodPicker` component with expand/collapse |
| **Validation** | | | |
| 1 | Show only available methods for address + seller | ✅ Pass | `shippingService.ts` pre-filters by zone + weight threshold |
| 2 | Cannot proceed without method selection | ✅ Pass | Default auto-selected; revalidation guard blocks stale |
| 3 | Selected method revalidated before placement | ✅ Pass | `handlePlaceOrder()` loops `shippingResults` vs `selectedMethods` |
| **System Processing** | | | |
| 1 | Fetch methods from `shipping_zones` filtered by GPS zones | ✅ Pass | Done in `shippingService.ts` L368-387 |
| 2 | Filter: same-day NCR-only, bulky by weight threshold | ✅ Pass | Filtered before reaching UI |
| 3 | Save method per seller in checkout payload | ✅ Pass | `shippingBreakdown[]` with method key + label |
| 4 | Update fee/ETA/totals on selection | ✅ Pass | `perStoreShippingFees` useMemo + `grandTotal` chain |
| 5 | Final revalidation at checkout | ✅ Pass | Stale method alert + block |
| **Display** | | | |
| 1 | Show courier name, fee, ETA per option | ✅ Pass | `MethodRow`: label + `₱fee · X-X days` |
| 2 | Selected method visible under seller group | ✅ Pass | Green highlight + check icon |
| 3 | Loading indicator during fetch | ✅ Pass | Shimmer placeholder |
| **Edge Cases** | | | |
| 1 | Method unavailable | ✅ Pass | Alert blocks place-order |
| 2 | No methods | ✅ Pass | "No shipping options available" gray card |
| 3 | Fetch failure | ✅ Pass | Red error card with message |

**Score: 18 ✅ / 0 🟡 / 0 ❌ — April 15: BX-09-002 IMPLEMENTED**

