### BX-09-003 — Show Estimated Delivery Time

| # | Criteria | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Flow** | | | |
| 1 | Buyer selects shipping method | ✅ Pass | `ShippingMethodPicker` in checkout |
| 2 | System calculates ETA | ✅ Pass | `shippingService.ts` generates `estimatedDays` string |
| 3 | Buyer reviews ETA before placing order | ✅ Pass | ETA shown in method picker: `₱fee · 3-5 days` |
| **Validation** | | | |
| 1 | ETA corresponds to selected method + destination | ✅ Pass | Each method has its own `estimated_days_min/max` from DB |
| 2 | ETA per seller group in multi-seller checkout | ✅ Pass | One picker per seller group, each shows own ETA |
| **System Processing** | | | |
| 1 | Retrieve ETA from courier logic/SLA | ✅ Pass | `shipping_zones.estimated_days_min/max` → formatted string |
| 2 | Refresh ETA on address/method change | ✅ Pass | Debounced recalc + instant method switch |
| 3 | Save ETA in checkout data | ✅ Pass | `order_shipments.estimated_days_text` persisted |
| **Display** | | | |
| 1 | ETA in readable format ("2-4 business days") | ✅ Pass | Generated by `shippingService.ts` |
| 2 | ETA near selected shipping option | ✅ Pass | Inline in `ShippingMethodPicker` |
| 3 | ETA visible in order details post-placement | ✅ Pass | Buyer `OrderDetailScreen` fetches `order_shipments` |
| **Edge Cases** | | | |
| 1 | No ETA → show "Delivery estimate unavailable" | ✅ Pass | Fallback in method picker |
| 2 | Missing ETA doesn't break checkout | ✅ Pass | `estimatedDays ?? 'N/A'` in payload |
| 3 | ETA refreshes after changes | ✅ Pass | Debounce triggers full recalc |

**Score: 14 ✅ / 0 🟡 / 0 ❌ — April 15: BX-09-003 IMPLEMENTED**

