## What Our BX-09-004 Work Gave the Other Stories

| Our Implementation | Stories It Enables |
|---|---|
| GPS coordinates on every address (map pin + "Use My Location") | BX-09-001 zone detection, BX-09-002 method filtering |
| PH phone validation (09/+63 format) | BX-09-001 courier booking validation |
| `validateCheckoutAddress()` with serviceability check | BX-09-001 pre-shipping validation gate |
| `AddressFormModal` shared component | All — consistent address entry everywhere |
| Address completeness enforcement (all 9 required fields) | BX-09-001 can trust address data for rate calculation |
| Per-field inline validation errors (yellow banner) | Buyer knows exactly which fields to fix before shipping calc runs |
| Separate red "Not Serviceable" banner with "Change Address" CTA | Clean signal for BX-09-001 to gate shipping calculation |
| Blue "Add Pin" nudge for missing GPS coordinates | Drives buyers to provide coords BX-09-001 needs for zone detection |
| `isPickup`/`isReturn` DB columns | BX-09-001 seller origin address identification |

---

## Implementation Order (Completed)

1. ~~**BX-09-004**~~ ✅ **DONE** — Address validation, GPS, phone, serviceability
2. ~~**BX-09-001**~~ ✅ **DONE** — Shipping engine wired, zone-based J&T math, debounced recalc
3. ~~**BX-09-002**~~ ✅ **DONE** — `ShippingMethodPicker` component, method revalidation guard, `order_shipments` persistence
4. ~~**BX-09-003**~~ ✅ **DONE** — ETA in checkout picker + order detail screen + DB persistence

